    <item>
      <title>高盛削减了对美国增长缓慢，欧佩克+政策缓慢的预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/goldman-cuts-oil-price-forecasts-on-slow-us-growth-opec-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团公司（Goldman Sachs Group Inc.）降低了其石油价格预测，因为关税降低了美国增长的前景，而欧佩克及其盟友则提高了产出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/goldman-cuts-oil-price-forecasts-on-slow-us-growth-opec-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 23:50:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着中国计划的增长，石油发展，红海风险增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-17</link>
      <description><![CDATA[顶级进口商中国表示将采取措施通过促进收入来恢复消费的第二天，石油上升了第二天，美国下令对也门的胡希斯进行新的袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-17</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 23:29:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股票在中国希望，美国期货滑倒：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/asia-to-extend-stock-rally-on-new-chinese-measures-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股票攀升后，中国承诺要恢复消费的更多步骤。美国财政部长斯科特·贝斯特（Scott Bessent）驳斥了该市场最近的健康状况，因此美国股票期货滑行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/asia-to-extend-stock-rally-on-new-chinese-measures-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 22:27:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>持续不必担心市场，呼吁更正健康</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/bessent-says-he-s-not-worried-about-market-corrections-healthy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长斯科特·贝斯特（Scott Bessent）是前对冲基金经理，他说，由于美国试图重塑其经济政策，他并不担心最近的经济下滑，从股票市场擦掉了数万亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/bessent-says-he-s-not-worried-about-market-corrections-healthy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 15:22:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巨大的美国风暴产生龙卷风，野火，至少有32人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-16/tornadoes-wildfires-and-blinding-dust-sweep-across-u-s-as-massive-storm-leaves-at-least-32-dead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰勒敦（Tylertown），密西西比州（AP）＆Mdash;多个美国各州的异常恶毒和破坏性的天气产生了剧烈的龙卷风，蒙蔽了沙尘暴和快速移动的野火，至少有37人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-16/tornadoes-wildfires-and-blinding-dust-sweep-across-u-s-as-massive-storm-leaves-at-least-32-dead</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 05:46:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
